data.description: Seller agrees to contribute $3,000 towards buyers closing costs. Spacious 5 bedroom/3 bathroom split level home with owner’s suite on the main level located in Kingswood Shoals. As you enter the home you notice the natural light flooding the room. To the right is the sunroom which may also be used as a dining room which opens to a great room and fireplace. The kitchen with eat-in dining area has a view to the great room. The laundry room is located off the kitchen and includes additional storage. Located on the same level are two additional bedrooms and a hall bath. Downstairs you will find two bonus rooms which may be used as bedrooms, office, or media room. The basement features an entertainment room equipped with a bar, and access to a full bathroom. Outside the fenced in and private backyard provides an oasis to entertain and/or garden while keeping your tools in an outside shed. Conveniently located near shopping, restaurants, schools and more.
